{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationProtocol"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/applicationprotocol\/addoption(group:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Adds a [OptionGroup](\/\/documentation\/glib\/optiongroup to the commandline handling of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationProtocol\/addOption(group:)"},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO19ApplicationProtocolPAAE9addOption5groupyqd___t4GLib0e5GroupC0Rd__lF","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","title":"addOption(group:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addOption","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"GLibOptionGroupT","kind":"genericParameter"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"text":"group","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GLibOptionGroupT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addOption"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"GLibOptionGroupT"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"group","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GLibOptionGroupT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"GLibOptionGroupT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OptionGroupProtocol","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib19OptionGroupProtocolP"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This function is comparable to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_option_context_add_group()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Unlike ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_application_add_main_option_entries()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", this function does","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"not deal with ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"arg_data"},{"text":" and never transmits options to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"primary instance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The reason for that is because, by the time the options arrive at the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"primary instance, it is typically too late to do anything with them."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Taking the GTK option group as an example: GTK will already have been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"initialised by the time the [Application](\/\/documentation\/gio\/application\/oncommandline(flags:handler:) handler runs."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In the case that this is not the first-running instance of the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"application, the existing instance may already have been running for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"a very long time.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This means that the options from [OptionGroup](\/\/documentation\/glib\/optiongroup are only really usable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the case that the instance of the application being run is the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"first instance.  Passing options like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"--display="},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"--gdk-debug=","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on future runs will have no effect on the existing primary instance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Calling this function will cause the options in the supplied option"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group to be parsed, but it does not cause you to be “opted in” to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"new functionality whereby unrecognized options are rejected even if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"handlesCommandLine","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" was given."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationProtocol":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ApplicationProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationprotocol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"code":"GApplication","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the core class for application support."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationProtocol","title":"ApplicationProtocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ApplicationProtocol","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationProtocol/addOption(group:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"addOption(group:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Adds a [OptionGroup](\/\/documentation\/glib\/optiongroup to the commandline handling of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationProtocol\/addOption(group:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addOption"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"GLibOptionGroupT","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"group","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GLibOptionGroupT"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationprotocol\/addoption(group:)"}}}